    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i dont mean like getting drunk or anything lol. just a small glass to take the edge off. i feel like it would actually help me relax more so i dont have to take a higher dose of the diazepam. if it's just a little bit, is it really that risky?",
